setting up development environment
    - mac
        - brew install osx-cross/avr/avr-gcc
        - brew install avrdude

    - rustup toolchain install nightly-2021-01-07
        - https://github.com/Rahix/avr-hal/issues/124

troubleshooting
    - if problem building, LLVM:
        - https://github.com/Rahix/avr-hal/issues/124
        - also try adding toolchain file
            - https://github.com/Rahix/avr-hal/issues/124#issuecomment-795676690
            - this worked for me!

binary in either target/avr-.../debug|release
